'''Randy Post''' a.k.a. '''R. K. Post''' (b. [[September 28]], [[1960s|1968]]) is an artist who provided illustrations for several sourcebooks and reference books, including:
{{Mediacat|imagecat=Images by R. K. Post}}
*''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''
*''[[The New Jedi Order Sourcebook]]''
*''[[Power of the Jedi Sourcebook]]''
*''[[Ultimate Alien Anthology]]''
*[[The Essential Guide to Alien Species (real-world book)|''The Essential Guide to Alien Species'']]
*''[[Ultimate Adversaries]]''
*''[[Jedi Academy Training Manual]]''

